oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Performance - Songwriters in the Round - 2014-05-24
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Songwriter round titled Miranda as Muse. Performances by songwriters Nicolle Gaylon; Natalie Hemby; Jimmy Robbins from the Ford Theater at the Country Music Hall of Fame and Museum on May 24, 2014. Presented in support of the exhibit Miranda Lambert
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Nicolle Gaylon; Natalie Hemby; Jimmy Robbins;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dcterms:tableOfContents: Performances include; Baggage Claim (Natalie Hemby) -- We Were Us (Nicolle Gaylon and Jimmy Robbins) -- Girls (Natalie Hemby) -- Virginia Bluebell (Natalie Hemby) -- Priscilla (Natalie Hemby or Nicolle Gaylon with Jimmy Robbins) -- Platinum (Natalie Hemby or Nicolle Gaylon) -- White Liar (Natalie Hemby) -- Babies Makin' Babies (Natalie Hemby or Nicolle Gaylon) -- It Ain't Pretty (Nicolle Gaylon) -- Downtown (Natalie Hemby) -- Sure Be Cool if You Did (Jimmy Robbins) -- Automatic (Nicolle Gaylon or Natalie Hemby)
